decks.notes: This deck revolves around the commander Sai, Master Thopterist, who creates Thopter tokens whenever you cast an artifact spell. The main goal of the deck is to flood the board with Thopter tokens and overwhelm the opponent with their sheer numbers. It utilizes various artifacts and artifact synergies to create a swarm of Thopters while also disrupting the opponent's game plan. The deck includes cards like Urza, Lord High Artificer, Tezzeret the Seeker, and Whir of Invention to tutor and search for key artifacts. It also features cards like Memory Lapse, Spell Pierce, and Counterspell to control the opponent's spells and disrupt their strategy. The deck aims to be aggressive and maintain board presence through the Thopter tokens while also having control elements to protect itself.
